name: Scattered House
description:
My "Photographic Art" are unique images created from my own photographs, each image is a well-composed photo to which I later apply Retouching such as Artistic Filters to give it different textures, Saturation to exaggerate the colors and Brightness, Contrast and Adjustments. Lighting Points and Shadows.

These is the artistic proposal that I carry in my heart and for which I wish to be recognized. My subjects are very varied and range from Nature, Animals, Plants, Landscapes, Urban Environment, Selfies, Portraits, Abstractions, Toy Art, Agriculture, Sunsets and whatever I can think of.

My name is Fran Afonso and I started as a photography hobbyist more than 10 years ago, then I studied Audiovisual Sciences and became a Professional. I am one of the two Directors of the Project "Sembrando un País" (SUP) and to this I owe my username.
